1. *Besan* sam zbog lošeg vremena. (I'm *angry* because of the bad weather.)
2. *Besna* mačka je ugrizla moga sina. (An *angry* cat bit my son.)
3. Mama je bila *besna* kada sam joj rekao da sam dobio jedinicu. (Mom was *angry* when I told her I got an F.)
4. Ne možeš proći pored psa kada je *besan*. (You can't pass by a dog when it's *angry*.)
5. *Besne* reči su mi izašle iz usta. (I spoke *angry* words.)
6. Videla sam ga kako *besno* vozi automobil. (I saw him driving the car *furiously*.)
7. *Besno* je tresnuo vratima kada je otišao iz kuće. (He slammed the door *angrily* when he left the house.)
8. Njegov *bes* se nije smirio ni posle sat vremena. (His *anger* didn't subside even after an hour.)
9. Nisam znao da će ta vest izazvati toliko *besa*. (I didn't know that news would cause so much *anger*.)
10. Uzalud pokušavaš da ga smiriš, on je u *besu*. (It's no use trying to calm him down, he's in a *rage*.)